title: Into the Wild.avi
description:
INTO THE WILD is inspired by the true story of Christopher McCandless (Emile Hirsch), a young man who abandons his life of comfort to prusue the freedom of life on the road, a quest that leads him to the Alaskan wilderness and the ultimate challenge of his life.  Screenplay and directed by Sean Penn and featuring an all-star cast including William Hurt, Marcia Gay Harden, Vince Vaughn, Catherine Keener and Hal Holbrook, INTO THE WILD is "as stirring, entertaining and steadfastly thrilling as it is beautiful." (Joe Morgenstern, The Wall Steet Journal)

My first up...hope all goes well and all enjoy this movie, it is excellant.
